    "title_en": "One more radiative-recoil correction to the Lamb shift in muonium",
    "abstract_en": "We calculate radiative-recoil contribution of order $Z^2α(Zα)^5(m/M)^2m$ to the Lamb shift in muonium. This correction is due to insertion of radiative photons in the heavy line in the two-photon exchange diagrams. Our calculations are inspired by a new round of precise $1S-2S$ and $2S-2P$ experiments currently in progress.",
